00:17:05,912 --> 00:17:09,094
I can say that we are a free-to-play friendly studio.

260
00:17:09,354 --> 00:17:11,076
So we are playing free-to-play games.

261
00:17:11,236 --> 00:17:12,357
We are analyzing those.

262
00:17:12,417 --> 00:17:13,657
We are talking about those.

263
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:19,842
It happens to be the standard monetization thing at the

