327
00:21:27,339 --> 00:21:32,682
during that we had the third round. And with that third round we saw that, yes,

328
00:21:33,918 --> 00:21:35,603
Finally, the game works.

329
00:21:35,743 --> 00:21:39,975
We have been able to improve and address all the biggest

330
00:21:40,055 --> 00:21:40,537
problems.

331
00:21:41,499 --> 00:21:42,141
And then we did.

332
00:21:43,276 --> 00:21:48,698
still before the worldwide launch, a very big kind of update for the game.

333
00:21:49,318 --> 00:21:52,299
And it was also very interesting because it was soft launch.

334
00:21:52,659 --> 00:21:56,981
It was interesting to cross-check that, hey, what is the metric saying

335
00:21:57,321 --> 00:21:59,062
and what is user testing round saying?

336
00:21:59,962 --> 00:22:03,584
