337
00:22:04,284 --> 00:22:04,924
So I think that...

338
00:22:06,545 --> 00:22:10,025
For a developer, this is kind of this magic if.

339
00:22:10,746 --> 00:22:12,866
And magic if comes from actor's work.

340
00:22:13,266 --> 00:22:16,327
If you are an actor, it's a very typical way of working.

341
00:22:16,967 --> 00:22:20,068
This, what if I would be that person

342
00:22:20,448 --> 00:22:22,388
in this particular situation?

343
00:22:22,788 --> 00:22:23,749
How would I feel?

344
00:22:23,869 --> 00:22:24,769
How would I act?

345
00:22:25,369 --> 00:22:28,130
So kind of changing that, that, hey, as a game developer,

346
00:22:28,710 --> 00:22:32,491
what if I am the player playing this game?

347
00:22:32,751 --> 00:22:33,791
How would I feel?

348
00:22:34,131 --> 00:22:35,971
Would I find this fun?

349
00:22:36,992 --> 00:22:40,294
So that changed our theme culture a lot.

350
00:22:40,774 --> 00:22:43,896
So nowadays when we are starting a new feature or new idea,

351
00:22:43,936 --> 00:22:48,138
