352
00:22:48,538 --> 00:22:50,279
As a player, I would like to.

353
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:54,602
So we always start from kind of point of view of a player.

354
00:22:54,942 --> 00:22:55,722
And that's great.

355
00:22:55,862 --> 00:22:59,765
So it's really playing, kind of putting players first.

356
00:23:02,859 --> 00:23:04,240
